ancpNasFullCompliance MODULE-COMPLIANCE STATUS current DESCRIPTION "The compliance statement for implementations of the ANCP-NAS-MIB.
When this MIB is implemented with support for read-write, then such an implementation can claim full compliance. Such devices can then be both monitored and configured with this MIB."
